<p><a name="References" id="References"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Creative_destruction&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6" title="Edit section: References">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">References</span></h2>
<div class="references-small">
<ol class="references">
<li id="cite_note-0"><b><a href="#cite_ref-0" title="">^</a></b> "the passion for destruction is a creative passion", <a href="http://www.marxists.org/reference/archive/bakunin/works/1842/reaction-germany.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.marxists.org/reference/archive/bakunin/works/1842/reaction-germany.htm" rel="nofollow">The Reaction in Germany</a>, Mikhail Bakunin, 1842</li>
